  "texts": [
    "Magnetic resonance imaging (MRI) scans, computed tomography (CT) results, microscopy images of stained tissue slides, and cytology analyses were among the primary sources of data used in AI-based applications 20.",
    "Images of serum, or urine droplet patterns, have not so far been analyzed in the context of BCa 30.",
    "Several studies focused on the physical-chemical properties of evaporation and the consequences/effects on the formation of various droplet patterns and their reproducibility 38.",
    "The behavior of droplet patterns is typical in pure liquids but has been found to be more complex in liquids containing multiple components 39.",
    "We had previously analyzed the effects of salt mixtures on droplet pattern formation of bovine serum albumin (BSA) solutions and discovered that mixtures induced formation of various complex patterns 26."
  ],
